    "\n",
    "- 🐍 Basic knowledge of Python and Keras. \n",
    "\n",
    "- 🧠 TensorFlow installed in your Python environment. \n",
    "\n",
    "- 📁 A data set of fruit images organized in subdirectories for each class. \n",
    "<br>",
    "\n\n",
